name: remap property names
Earthquake !!!
info:
Press the button on the `inject` node to get the list of earthquakes from the USGS public API.

This returns a CSV - which we then parse using the `CSV` node into individual objects.

These are then passed through a `function` to remap the property names into ones 
suitable for the map node, and passed to the `web-socket` out node.

The map will be served at http://localhost:1880/worldmap .
You will need to zoom out :-)
